PLOT
When world-famous air racer Dusty learns that his engine is damaged and 
he may never race again, he must shift gears and is launched into the 
world of aerial firefighting. Dusty joins forces with veteran fire and 
rescue helicopter Blade Ranger and his team, a bunch of all-terrain 
vehicles known as The Smokejumpers. Together, the fearless team battles 
a massive wildfire, and Dusty learns what it takes to become a true 
hero.
